>>>INFO

https://riptutorial.com/ru/redis

https://netpoint-dc.com/blog/nastroika-redis-docker-dlya-produktovogo-ispolzovaniya/

https://www.ionos.com/community/hosting/redis/using-redis-in-docker-containers/

>>>TO RUN THIS
    sudo docker run --restart=always -d --name redis_1 \
       -v /opt/redis/etc/redis.conf:/usr/local/etc/redis/redis.conf \
       -v /opt/redis/data:/data \
       -p 127.0.0.1:6379:6379 redis redis-server \
       /usr/local/etc/redis/redis.conf

>>>TO CONNECT WITH COMMANDLINE INSTALL IT
sudo apt install redis-tools

>>>CONNECT WITH REDDIS
sudo redis-cli
